  "detailed_description": "Sorcevival is a horde survival game in which you must battle ever-growing waves of enemies while enhancing and customizing your spells. Survive for 15 minutes, conquer Bosses, and acquire mana to upgrade your character.<br><br>All your spells can be tailored using a talent tree, and each time you defeat an elite, you will gain a rune that allows you to do anything from altering the spell's element to granting it unique synergies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2673240/extras/866715205f91af473fe92c1a187e41f8.poster.avif?t=1745443619\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2673240/extras/866715205f91af473fe92c1a187e41f8.webm?t=1745443619\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2673240/extras/866715205f91af473fe92c1a187e41f8.mp4?t=1745443619\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Vanquish Bosses and obtain Active abilities to employ in moments of utmost need.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2673240/extras/0a32c9fa583d5f572cca482e3372f37c.poster.avif?t=1745443619\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2673240/extras/0a32c9fa583d5f572cca482e3372f37c.webm?t=1745443619\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2673240/extras/0a32c9fa583d5f572cca482e3372f37c.mp4?t=1745443619\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Utilize the acquired mana to enhance your stats and unlock new items, spells, runes and relics.",
